    <h1 class="page-title">Grants and Projects</h1>
    <p class="page-intro">
      Active and ongoing projects focused on scaling genomic medicine, improving variant interpretation,
      and strengthening translational deployment in healthcare.
    </p>
  </header>

  <section class="section grid two">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Current Funding Themes</h2>
      <ul class="list-plain">
        <li>Clinical genomics implementation programs</li>
        <li>Population-scale sequencing integration</li>
        <li>AI-assisted interpretation and decision support</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h2>Leadership and Collaboration</h2>
      <ul class="list-plain">
        <li>Program leadership in SG100K-aligned efforts</li>
        <li>Cross-institutional projects with clinical partners</li>
        <li>Bioinformatics capacity building and deployment</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="section card">
    <h3>Detailed grant list</h3>
    <p>
      A detailed list of active grants, project periods, and leadership roles will be added in the next
      content update.
    </p>
  </section>
